            <p>
               Sometimes achievement and overcoming challenges will occur within the minutiae of daily living and are often unnoticed by the PwMS and others. Encourage 
                the PwMS to keep a journal of things achieved in daily life; this can facilitate new insights into personal ability and capacity.
            </p>
             <p>We often do not know just how wonderful we are!</p>
